✊🏿✊🏽✊🏼✊🏾Here’s a little something about the history of International Women’s Day!

We believe this day can be an opportunity to celebrate women’s achievements from all over the world. It is also important, however, to acknowledge the ongoing political, social, economic and cultural challenges that women still have to face (For example: only 6 countries give women equal legal work rights as men.)

These are of course ongoing issues that can not be solved in a single day. So we would like to continue this mindset for the entire year (and for all of eternity for that matter) to keep encouraging each other to fight for gender equality and to empower women and girls everywhere.

🥁Today is the very last day to apply for 𝐏𝐨𝐩𝐫𝐨𝐧𝐝𝐞 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟐! @popronde is the biggest traveling music festival in the Netherlands, that supports and represents the next generation pop musicians. Our member @joaodegroot is part of the organization & programming team:

"We try to give an accurate representation of what's happening in the Dutch live music scene, taking the definition of pop music as broad as possible. Hiphop, metal and even neo-classical acts deserve a spot in our yearly selection. Participation leads to more experience on stage and it will boost your network."

So… do you have enough material to give a live performance of at least 30 minutes? And would you like to be a part of this crazy ride? Check their website and get on board!

🎥: Mees van Keeken
🎵: @youngrubbi - Verdrinken in het zwembad
